          <h2 style="margin:0;">Policy Processing Tracker</h2>
          <div style="font-size:12px; color:var(--text-muted); margin-top:4px;">Expected Completion: <b>24 Jun 2026</b> <span style="margin:0 8px;">·</span> Processing Age: <b>5 Days</b></div>
        </div>
